# M7 RAG 知识库：Milvus + Ollama Embedding

## 里程碑

**M7** — 理财静态知识库（`agent/knowledge/finance/`）向量化存入 Milvus；Agent `search_knowledge` + REST 检索接入。

## 关联 Skill

| Skill | 用途 |
|-------|------|
| [add-api-endpoint](../Skills/add-api-endpoint/SKILL.md) | `GET /knowledge/search` |
| [http-integration-test](../Skills/http-integration-test/SKILL.md) | knowledge_test |
| [local-dev](../Skills/local-dev/SKILL.md) | Milvus + Ollama 本地验收 |
| [extract-ai-knowledge](../Skills/extract-ai-knowledge/SKILL.md) | `docs/knowledge/rag.md` |

## 范围

### 交付文件

| 文件 | 说明 |
|------|------|
| `agent/knowledge/finance/` | 理财知识 10 篇 Markdown |
| `agent/rag/` | embedding / indexer / milvus / retriever |
| `agent/skills/knowledge.py` | `search_knowledge` skill |
| `docker-compose.yml` | Milvus standalone |
| `common/env.py` | MILVUS_URI、OLLAMA_EMBEDDING_MODEL、RAG_TOP_K |
| `server/api/knowledge.py` | REST 检索 |
| `examples/04_rag_knowledge_demo.py` | 独立 demo |
| `docs/knowledge/rag.md` | 知识点（含 Embedding 定义与使用场景） |

## 知识点文档

| slug | 文件 | 验收 |
|------|------|------|
| `rag` | `docs/knowledge/rag.md` | README 索引 status → done |

## 运行命令

```bash
docker compose up -d
ollama pull nomic-embed-text
.venv/bin/python3.14 -m agent.rag.index
.venv/bin/python3.14 server/main.py
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" "http://127.0.0.1:8000/knowledge/search?q=备用金"
.venv/bin/python3.14 -m pytest agent/rag/indexer_test.py server/api/knowledge_test.py -v
```

## 验收标准

- [x] `agent/knowledge/finance/` 10 篇理财知识文档
- [x] Milvus docker-compose 可起
- [x] 索引 + 检索 API 可用
- [x] Agent 注册 `search_knowledge`
- [x] `docs/knowledge/rag.md` 存在
